### ============================================================
### admin.rest — System and administrative endpoints
### ============================================================

### ---- Variables (change host/port here to switch environments) ----
@host = localhost
@port = 3000
@userId = 3000
@baseAPI = http://{{host}}:{{port}}/api

### ============================================================
### HEALTH & SYSTEM CHECKS
### ============================================================

###
### Health Check
### @name healthCheck
GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/health

###
### API Docs (Swagger UI)
### Open: http://localhost:3000/docs
GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/docs.json

### ============================================================
### ADMIN - GET/PATCH/POST /api/admin/...
### ============================================================

###
### Get System Metrics (últimas 24 horas)
### @name adminMetrics
GET {{baseAPI}}/admin/metrics

###
### Get System Health Status
### @name adminHealth
GET {{baseAPI}}/admin/health

###
### Reset User Password (Admin Only)
### @name adminResetPassword
POST {{baseAPI}}/admin/users/{{userId}}/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nueva_password": "new_secure_password_123"
}
